<h3>autoPlay</h3>

<p>Automatically advances to the next cell.</p>

<p>Auto-playing will pause when mouse is hovered over, and resume when mouse is hovered off. Auto-playing will stop when the gallery is clicked or a cell is selected.</p>

``` js
// values
// autoPlay: 

autoPlay: true
// advance cells every 3 seconds

autoPlay: 1500 // {Number}
// advance cells ever {Number} milliseconds
// 1500 will advance cells ever 1.5 seconds
```

